{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你是不是在奇怪，我为什么要笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为你根本不是人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是个很忠实的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你说他忠实？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他至少对自己做的事很忠实，他的毒药的确没有失效过一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "所以你更应该感激我，若不是我，现在死的就是你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我倒的确从未想到过他也会卖我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你若从未想过，怎么会早已准备好对付他的法子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为我也是个很忠实的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你对什么忠实？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "对我自己。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你怎么从来不说我也很忠实？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为你对你自己也不忠实，你常常都在出卖自己，你自己出卖自己。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "但我却从来未出卖过你，也从来没有骗过你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为你知道没有人能骗得过我的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "所以你在我面前，也是个老实人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你说你的朋友都已走了，他们果然不在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "现在我只想知道，你是对钱比较忠实，还是对我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "那得看情形。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "怎么看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "通常我是对钱忠实些，但现在是对你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "很好，拿来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "拿什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "桌子下面有几块石板是松的，下面有个地窖。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你以为我看不出来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你既已看出来，为什么还不去拿？东西就在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "我去拿出来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "speaker_name": "催命符",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这次，你总该明白我为什么要笑了吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不明白。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你知不知道我是用什么杀他的？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "那就是我从他那里学来的游魂刺。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他刚用赤练蛇的毒，毒死了赤练蛇，我立刻就用他的刺，刺死了他，这么有趣的事，我想不笑都不行。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我只奇怪，他怎会将这一着教给你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为他并没有完全将诀窍教给我，知道我永远学不好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你的确没有他快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "那差得远了，所以我虽然学会，却还是没有用，根本不能用来对付别人。游魂刺还是他的独门兵器。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "既然没有用，你何必学？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "并不是完全没有用，只有一种用处，只能用来对付一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他自己。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你不能用来对付别人，却能用来对付他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "天下就有很多事，都是这么奇怪的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你不懂的事还多着哩。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我故意单独留下你和赤练蛇在一起，为的就是要让你们有机会说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "原来你是故意走的。",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我先故意说出他最见不得人的事，然后再走开，故意要他气得半死；你看到那种机会当然不肯错过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你知道我会想法子说动他，要他出卖你们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "并不是你说动他的，他早已有了这意思，只不过一直没有机会而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你故意让给他这机会，然后就去叫崔老大提防着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我也知道崔老大早已有对付他的法子，他只要一出手，就得死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你算得很准。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这点我倒也不必太谦虚。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这件事我总算明白了，还有呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你知不知道崔老大最大的秘密是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他的耳朵并不灵，简直跟聋子差不许多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "但我跟他说话，声音并不太大，他却都听得见。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "那只因为他看你的嘴唇动作，就能看出你说的是什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这的确是个秘密。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这秘密除了我之外，没有别人知道。就因为他的耳朵不灵，所以永远不肯走在任何人前面，他生怕别人从背后暗算他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这倒并不是因为他比别人小心，只不过因为他听不见暗器的风声，若有人从背后暗算他，他根本没法子闪避。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "若是风声很尖锐，他当然还是听得见的，但若有人从背后慢慢地给他一下子，那他就非死不可了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "一点也不错，所以，我用那永远也学不好的游魂刺来对付他，反而再好也没有了啊。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你也算准了他一听到东西在那里，就忍不住会赶到前面去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "若在别人面前，他也许还能沉得住气，还会提防着；但跟我在一起的时候，他总是会比平时疏忽些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为他总认为我是在倚靠着他，总认为他若死了，我也活不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他也总认为没有人能骗过他……",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "的确没有人能骗过他，他自己能骗过自己。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你说他自己在骗自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "不会自我陶醉的男人，天底下还没有几个，男人若是不自我陶醉，女人还能混么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你的确算得很准，也看得很准。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但我却看错了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我始终认为你是不会说谎的，想不到你若说起谎话来，简直可以骗死人不赔命。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我说了什么谎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你说东西就在桌子下面，这是不是说谎？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但却只有我一个人知道你在说谎，因为世上只有我才知道东西到底藏在哪里。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你应该知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "说老实话，你刚才有没有想到过，东西是我拿走的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "没有想到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我什么都没有想到，什么都不知道，我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "一个人不能太得意。无论谁若觉得没有人能骗他，他就是自己在骗自己。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这句话的意思就是说，你若能设计出一个圈套来害别人，别人就也能设计出一个圈套来害他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "王动，我知道你一直是个很公平的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他本来就是的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "要怎么样公平？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "刚才我已将我的圈套说了出来，现在你呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "刚才你是从哪里说起的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "从我给你机会让你单独和赤练蛇说话的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么跟他说那些话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "所以我一定要从你们三个人中，找出谁是拿走那些东西的人来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你跟赤练蛇说那些话，为的就是要试探他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不错，他若是拿走那些东西的人，就绝不会那么做了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你怎么知道那人不是大蜈蚣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他假如是的，就不会那么冒险——有了几千万两身价的人，坐在屋檐下会生怕有瓦会掉下来打破他的头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你为什么不说得简单些？千金之子，不坐垂堂，这句话我也听得懂的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "知道那些东西藏处的只有五个人，除掉三个，就只剩下你和崔老大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但你还是不能确定，我和崔老大究竟谁才是真正拿走那些东西的人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "那时我还不能确定，但我已有把握，迟早总会找出人来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你真有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "第一，我知道赤练蛇绝不是崔老大的敌手，只要一有举动，就必死无疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你倒也看得很准。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "第二，我知道你和崔老大之间，也必定有个人要死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为无论谁拿走那些东西，都绝不会让另一个人活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为我们五个人之中，只要还有一个人活着，他就不能安心享受那笔财富，现在五个人等于只剩下一个，正是他最好的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这机会的确太好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他已等了很久，好容易才等到这机会，当然绝不肯轻易错过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "若换了你，也一定舍不得错过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "何况以前他还可以将责任推在我身上，现在既已找到了我，他的秘密就迟早要被揭穿，就算他不想杀别人，别人也一定要杀他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我本来的确不愿他们找到你，可是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你们的确都是他的好朋友，的确是比他以前那些朋友好得多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你算来算去，早已算准了最后必定只有一个人剩下来，也算准了他就是拿走那些东西的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这算法本来就好像一加一等于二那么简单。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "难道你赴约去的时候就已算准了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "若非如此，我们怎么能放心让他去赴约？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我早就该想到的，我早就看出你们不是那种看见朋友有危险就偷偷溜走的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他们的确不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但是我有几点想不通。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你可以问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你中计被擒，难道也是故意的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我只知道那地方绝不会突然冒出个荒坟来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你故意被他们抓住，难道不怕他们当时就杀了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "怕总是有点怕的。",
      "tone": "坦然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但你还是照样要去做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为我已猜到，你们绝不会就只为了要杀我而来，一定还另有目的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你已猜出是什么目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "所以你就叫他们在这里等着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你有把握能诱我们到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "只有一点，不太多。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但你还是要这么样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "一个人若只肯做绝对有把握的事，那么他就连一样事都做不成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "因为世上本没有绝对有把握的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你要他们藏在这里，难道就不怕事先被我们发现么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这种机会很少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这得分几种情形来说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "第一种情况是，三个人都同在这里的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这时三个人之中，至少有两个以为藏宝就在桌下，当然绝不肯让别人先得手的；就算有人要过来看看，也必定有人会阻止；所以在这种情况下，他们必是安全的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "第二种情况呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "那时已只剩下两个人了，就譬如说是你和崔老大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "不用譬如，本来就是我们。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "那时你已决心不让崔老大再活着，他就算想要来看看，你也必定会先下手，所以在这种情况下，他们也是安全的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "第三种情况当然是已只剩下我一个人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "那点你穴道的地方，还是被点住的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我若先发现他们藏在那里，岂非还可以先把他们封死在里面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "可是你明知藏宝不在那里，怎么会过去看？你根本连注意都不会注意，所以在这种情况下，他们也是安全的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你真的算得那么精，那么准？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "假的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "人算不如天算，谁也不能将一件事算得万无一失的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但你还是冒这个险？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这本是我们的孤注一掷，最后一击。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你们的胆子也未免太大了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我们的胆子并不大，计谋也没有你们精密，甚至连力量都比你们薄弱些，这一战，我们本该败的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "但你们却胜了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "那只因为我们有样你们没有的东西。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "友情。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这样东西虽然是看不见摸不着，但力量之大，却是你们永远也梦想不到的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我们敢拼命，敢冒险，也因为我们知道自己并不是孤立无助的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "一个人若知道自己无论在什么情况下，都有真正的朋友站在他一边，和他同生共死、共患难，他立刻就会变得有了勇气，有了信心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我本来也想要他们走，但他们只说了一句话，就令我改变了主意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他们说了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他们告诉我，我们要活，就快快乐乐的活在一起；要死，也痛痛快快的死在一起；无论是死是活，都没什么了不起。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你从来没有朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "那绝不是因为朋友不要你，而是因为你不要朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "用你自己的真心诚意。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你们三个人中，只要有半分真心诚意，今天就一定还快快乐乐的活着。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 692
    }
  ],
